reviewText: Horrible!!!  Do not watch, no matter how much your child begs you!  You will want to slit your throat.  Spend your money on the REAL thing!
Title: Beauty and the Beast

reviewText: This is not the greatest version of Beauty & the Beast but my young granddaughter really likes it.  She watched it repeatedly when it was on TV so I thought I would buy it for her.  Fair price, too, to have her sit quietly and look at a video.
Title: Beauty and the Beast

reviewText: Isn't what my granddaughter hoped for. She was very, very disappointed and so was I. Not Disney quality. Very disappointed.
Title: Beauty and the Beast

reviewText: my 3 yo is going through a B and the B phase and wile i wait for the Disney version to get to me from ebay, i ordered this. For the money it makes her happy, but it is poorly done. reminiscent of Hannah Barbera in the 703. YUCK. but little one is happy so it works. if it was more $ id be very unhappy.
summary: horrible, but the 3 yo loves it
